Package: tidyspec
Type: Package
Title: Tidyspec: Spectroscopy Analysis Using The Tidy Data Philosophy
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: person("Marcel", "Ferreira", , "marcel.ferreira@unesp.br", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3445-0945"))
Maintainer: Marcel Ferreira <marcel.ferreira@unesp.br>
Description: The tidyspec package enables the analysis of spectroscopy data, 
    including IR, Raman, and NMR, using the tidy data framework from the 
    tidyverse. It provides functions for transformation, normalization, 
    baseline correction, smoothing, derivatives, and visualization, making 
    spectral analysis more structured and reproducible.
